      <title>祖马政党在南非选举活动中大力推行财富税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/zuma-s-party-touts-wealth-tax-in-south-african-election-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非前总统雅各布·祖马支持的一个政党表示，预计将在 5 月 29 日选举后入阁，并计划在上任后通过增加资本利得和遗产税来增加额外的国家收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/zuma-s-party-touts-wealth-tax-in-south-african-election-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 15:58:14 GMT</pubDate>
